The paper deals with active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes a novel active learning model and discusses the transfer of active learning experience across datasets. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
